\begin_inset Formula $\Delta_{\text{SO}}$
\end_inset

.
 Hence, we have that 
\begin_inset Formula $(\alpha_{\text{R}})_{\alpha\beta}\approx a_{0}t_{0}\Delta_{\text{SO}}/\Delta_{\text{sb}}\langle\tilde{\tilde{\alpha}}|\mathcal{H}_{\text{R}}|\tilde{\tilde{\beta}}\rangle\equiv\alpha_{0}^{\text{R}}\langle\tilde{\tilde{\alpha}}|\mathcal{H}_{\text{R}}|\tilde{\tilde{\beta}}\rangle$
\end_inset

 with 
