\begin_layout Standard
Before diving straight into the case in Eq.(
\begin_inset Formula $\text{\ref{eq:H_BdG}}$
\end_inset

), let us start with a simpler systems and gradually ramp up to the general
 case in order to gain some insight of the problem.
 For starters, let us consider instead an infinite nanowire (again, infinite
 in the sense that 
\begin_inset Formula $\ell\gg\xi$
\end_inset

) in the normal regime, i.e in the absence of SC proximity 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta=0$
\end_inset

.
